  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>... that <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a> is partially inspired by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tiberius\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Tiberius\">Tiberius Caesar</a>, particularly <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Baker_(actor)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:George Baker (actor)\">George Baker</a>'s portrayal in <i><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/I,_Claudius_(TV_series)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:I, Claudius (TV series)\">I, Claudius</a></i>?<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Did_you_know/95&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/92nd_Street_Y\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:92nd Street Y\">92nd Street Y</a>: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/Vcy-EhkHXnE?t=1h1m37s\">Game of Thrones Mastermind George R. R. Martin: The World of Ice and Fire</a> (Oct 26, 2014)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/Not_a_Blog\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Not a Blog\">Not a Blog</a>: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://grrm.livejournal.com/310379.html?thread=17